title: 4,500-year-old chamber discovered in Great Pyramid - but specialists are puzzled over its function
description: A new chamber dating back some 4,500 years has been uncovered in one of the Great Pyramids in Egypt.

title: Firefighters battle high-rise blaze in popular Hong Kong shopping district
description: Firefighters have been battling a huge blaze at a high-rise building in a popular shopping area of Hong Kong.

title: 'We had children inside and we were the ones being attacked': Huwara residents reflect on night of violence
description: I've been to Huwara many times, but never seen it like this. Driving in feels like you're nearing the frontline of a war.

title: 'We're waiting for you': Gunmen leave menacing message for Messi after shooting at in-laws' supermarket
description: Gunman targeting a supermarket owned by Lionel Messi's parents-in-law left a threatening written message for the Argentina football star, police say.

title: Flamingos form friendship groups based on their personalities - study
description: Birds of the same feather group together but, within their flocks, flamingos form smaller cliques of like-minded individuals, a new study suggests.

title: Man survives 31 days in Amazon jungle by eating insects and drinking own urine
description: A Bolivian hunter survived 31 days in the Amazon jungle by eating insects and drinking his own urine.
